          Vanilla 6.2

          Wednesday, September 26, 2018 by admin

          Vanilla 6.2   Vanilla 6.2 is available for download. Vanilla 6.2
          comes with a set of new features, including but not limited to :
          GPRD compliancy, Vanilla Data Preparation, a new User module to
          work with any kind of data (text, excel, sql, Hadoop, Vanilla
          Architect, Vanilla Metadata), Vanilla Forms Editor, a simple
          integrated interface to create forms on sql data, Vanilla
          extension for LibreOffice, New set of features for WebDashboard,
          FlexBoard, Portal, Metadata, WebReport … 'Deployment of Vanilla
          6.2 has started for existing customers since Q3-2018, and we
          target 100% migration of our customers base by Q1-2019' said
          Patrick Beaucamp, Bpm-Conseil Ceo and Chairman. For more
          information on how we can help you to develop together your
          Business intelligence project, your Data Analysis and Mining
          projects, please contact us at info@bpm-conseil.com

