          The Document Foundation welcomes BPM Conseil to the project’s
          Advisory Board

          Friday, May 18, 2018 by admin

          The Document Foundation welcomes BPM Conseil to the project’s
          Advisory Board The Document Foundation (TDF) announced today
          that BPM-Conseil, a company focused on open source business
          intelligence based in Lyon (France), has joined the LibreOffice
          project’s Advisory Board. BPM-Conseil will develop the
          integration of LibreOffice with its business intelligence
          solutions Aklabox and Vanilla, and also create business
          intelligence related extensions for LibreOffice. More
          information can be found in the original post :
          https://blog.documentfoundation.org/blog/2018/05/18/bpm-conseil/

