          Vanilla Air - Vanilla Metadata

          Thursday, November 26, 2015 by CMA

          Vanilla Air supports Vanilla Metadata Vanilla Air, the Analytics
          & Predictive platform and part of Vanilla Smart Data, provides
          support for a wide range of data sources, including Hadoop hdfs
          files, Hadoop hbase, csv files, r dataset, any jdbc sql
          database; and now including Vanilla Metadata documents. It
          allows any Vanilla user to select columns using Metadata
          Explorer, to run simple analysis (including aggregate and olap
          view) from Vanilla portal and then, to push the Metadata view to
          Vanilla Air if he needs to run advanced analysis and use this
          Metadata data source inside any predictive model. BPM Team

