          Apache Flink

          Friday, October 09, 2015 by CMA

          Apache Flink BPM Teams use and integrate Apache Flink in our
          platforms for complex data distribution and computation in
          Hadoop environment. Apache Flink is a streaming data flow engine
          with several API for data distribution, computation on
          distributed architecture with lots of nice features like
          iterative computations. Together with Flink, Vanilla platforms -
          ETL and BI - can scale to meet customer's expectations in
          disruptive environment. Check out the Apache Flink Website BPM
          Team

