          Vanilla & Birt 4.5

          Monday, June 29, 2015 by CMA

          Vanilla & Birt 4.5 Vanilla integrated Birt 4.5 update and takes
          benefit of all the improvements. This update comes also with the
          adding of the Birt librairies (pool of resources such as
          connections, datasets or items) in the server part. This allows
          to design a report using Birt librairy and run it from Vanilla
          portal. More information on Birt : Birt WebSite BPM Team

