          Apache Drill Support

          Wednesday, June 24, 2015 by CMA

          Apache Drill Support Our development team integrated Apache
          Drill in Vanilla in order to offer brand new data retrieving
          opportunities for Big Data. Through this support, everyone can
          build reports, dashboards or cubes directly on text files stored
          on Hadoop using SQL language and taking advantage of Hadoop
          performance & cloud architecture. Apache Drill is a major
          release in the Apache Hadoop ecosystem. Integrated with Vanilla,
          it allows to access directly and with a SQL synthax data stored
          in HBase, HDFS, MongoDB or Hive in Hadoop environment. BPM Team

