          Apache Phoenix

          Wednesday, June 17, 2015 by CMA

          Apache Phoenix BPM Teams use and integrate Apache Phoenix in the
          platforms cores for data retrieving on top of Hadoop HBase.
          Apache Phoenix allows to query HBase data with relational layer
          with lots of SQL features. Phoenix powered Vanilla platforms -
          ETL and BI - making it easy to run complex distributed SQL
          statments on top of Hadoop. Check out the Apache Phoenix Website
          BPM Team

