          Vanilla and Spark

          Monday, May 25, 2015 by CMA

          Vanilla and Spark Our development team has developed package to
          store data inside Spark, opening new opportunities for developer
          to build complex analytical application using the combined power
          of Vanilla and Spark. Data stored in Hadoop environment can be
          analyzed thanks to Vanilla using Spark applications (Java and
          Scala support). Apache Spark is a fast and general engine for
          big data processing, with built-in modules for streaming, SQL,
          machine learning and graph processing. BPM Team

