          reporting and analysis to DataMining, we are proud to announce
          we have integrated R version 3.12 inside Vanilla. Vanilla
          platform provides methods and support to run R standard
          algorithms like cluster or decision tree analysis on top of any
          Vanilla Metadata document. This is another impressive
          demonstration of Open Source usage to offer disruptive platform
          in a scalable, innovative and performant way. BPM Team

