          Agila & Impala

          Wednesday, February 18, 2015 by CMA

          Agila & Impala Agila, the Web front-end platform for Big Data
          Analysis, has been updated with Cloudera Impala Support.
          Cloudera Impala has an SQL like synthax and a performant engine
          for data querying on top of Hive. It provides faster response
          time for any Impala queries on Hive database, including Olap
          queries. Agila is a nice place for querying your Hadoop data in
          an OLAP environment with Impala connectivity support ! BPM Team

