          2 New Vanilla Apps released

          Tuesday, November 15, 2011 by admin

          BPM-Conseil is proud to announce this new pre-release of Vanilla
          4.0. This release candidate (RC2) is available from our forge
          :http://forge.bpm-conseil.com/frs/?group_id=11  This new release
          features new state of the art functionalities such as :  -
          UnitedOlap, a new high-performance Olap engine providing the
          ability to design your cubes on different data sources (even
          excel) and featuring an advanced cache system to speed your
          cubes.  - Advanced clustering and load balancing for the
          VanillaRuntime, spread your tasks and treatments across
          different vanilla's.  - A new one stop VanillaViewer to view and
          interact with all your BI documents.  - A brand new portal,
          faster and leaner.  - Vanilla 4.0 RC1 improvements  - And many
          more improvements to overall user experience.  Enjoy this new
          RC2 version and go to the download link.

